snippet: The 50th volume of “Now That’s What I Call Music!” unseated the soundtrack to Disney’s “Frozen,” which spent 13 weeks atop the album chart.
abstract: The 50th volume of “Now That’s What I Call Music!” unseated the soundtrack to Disney’s “Frozen,” which spent 13 weeks atop the album chart.

headline.main: 'Now That's What I Call Music' Ends 'Frozen' Soundtrack's No. 1 Run
headline.print_headline: ‘Frozen’ Falls From Top Of Billboard Chart
